OBJECT Report 14000827 Bill of Lading Info. Lines Adv
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=07/01/20;
    Time=12:00:00 AM;
    Modified=Yes;
    Version List=SE0.55.13;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    CaptionML=ENU=Bill of Lading Info. Lines Adv;
    OnInitReport=BEGIN
                   CLEARALL;
                 END;

  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 6966;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table14000822;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Released,Summary Released,Posted)
                                 ORDER(Descending)
                                 WHERE(Released=FILTER(Yes));
               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  FormatAddress.BillOfLadingShipTo(ShipToAddress,"Bill of Lading");
                                  FormatAddress.BillOfLadingShipFrom(ShipFromAddress,"Bill of Lading");
                                  IncludePhoneNo(ShipToAddress,"Bill of Lading"."Ship-to Phone No.");
                                  IncludePhoneNo(ShipFromAddress,"Bill of Lading"."Ship-from Phone No.");
                                  IF "Bill of Lading"."Shipping Agent Code" <> '' THEN
                                    ShippingAgent.GET("Bill of Lading"."Shipping Agent Code");
                                  FOR i := 1 TO 3 DO
                                    ShippingPymtType[i] := '_______';
                                  IF "Bill of Lading"."Shipping Agent Code" <> '' THEN
                                    ShippingAgent.GET("Bill of Lading"."Shipping Agent Code");
                                  CASE "Bill of Lading"."Shipping Payment Type" OF
                                    "Bill of Lading"."Shipping Payment Type"::Prepaid:
                                      ShippingPymtType[1] := '___X___';
                                    "Bill of Lading"."Shipping Payment Type"::"Freight Collect":
                                      ShippingPymtType[2] := '___X___';
                                    "Bill of Lading"."Shipping Payment Type"::"Third Party",
                                    "Bill of Lading"."Shipping Payment Type"::Consignee:
                                      ShippingPymtType[3] := '___X___';
                                  END;
                                  IF "Bill of Lading"."COD Payment" THEN BEGIN
                                    CODAmt := "Bill of Lading"."COD Amount";
                                    CODCustCk := FORMAT(NOT ("Bill of Lading"."COD Cashiers Check"));
                                  END ELSE
                                    CODAmt := 0;
                                END;

               ReqFilterFields=No. }

    { 8178;1   ;Column  ;Bill_of_Lading_No_  ;
               SourceExpr="No." }

    { 5701;1   ;DataItem;CopyLoop            ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               NoLoops := ABS(NoCopies);
                               IF NoLoops <= 0 THEN
                                 NoLoops := 1;
                               CopyNo := 0;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  CurrReport.PAGENO := 1;

                                  IF CopyNo = NoLoops THEN
                                    CurrReport.BREAK
                                  ELSE
                                    CopyNo := CopyNo + 1;
                                  IF CopyNo = 1 THEN
                                    CLEAR(CopyTxt)
                                  ELSE
                                    CopyTxt := 'COPY';
                                END;
                                 }

    { 6455;2   ;DataItem;PageLoop            ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 WHERE(Number=CONST(1));
               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  BillOfLadingInfoLine.RESET;
                                  BillOfLadingInfoLine.SETRANGE("Bill of Lading No.","Bill of Lading"."No.");
                                  BillOfLadingInfoLine.SETRANGE(
                                    "Info. Line Type",BillOfLadingInfoLine."Info. Line Type"::"Cust. Order Info.");
                                  CustInfoCNT := BillOfLadingInfoLine.COUNT;

                                  CarInfoBillOfLadingInfoLine.RESET;
                                  CarInfoBillOfLadingInfoLine.SETRANGE("Bill of Lading No.","Bill of Lading"."No.");
                                  CarInfoBillOfLadingInfoLine.SETRANGE(
                                    "Info. Line Type",CarInfoBillOfLadingInfoLine."Info. Line Type"::"Commodity Info.");
                                  CarrierInfoCNT := CarInfoBillOfLadingInfoLine.COUNT;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 5444;3   ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 ORDER(Ascending);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               IF (CustInfoCNT = 0) AND (CarrierInfoCNT = 0) THEN
                                 Integer.SETRANGE(Number,1,0);
                               Integer.SETRANGE(Number,1,ReportLoop(CustInfoCNT,CarrierInfoCNT));
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  DeleteRecords;
                                  ClearValues;
                                  PageNumber := Number; //Added for RDLC

                                  IF Number = 1 THEN BEGIN
                                    IF CarInfoBillOfLadingInfoLine.FIND('-') THEN;
                                    IF BillOfLadingInfoLine.FIND('-') THEN;
                                    Lines := 6;
                                  END ELSE
                                    Lines := 15;
                                  IF CustInfoCNT >= Number THEN
                                    FOR i := 1 TO Lines DO BEGIN
                                      tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine1[i].TRANSFERFIELDS(BillOfLadingInfoLine);
                                      tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine1[i]."Line No." := BillOfLadingInfoLine."Line No." + 1;
                                      tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine1[i].INSERT;
                                      GrandWgt := GrandWgt + tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine1[i].Weight;
                                      GrandPkg := GrandPkg + tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine1[i]."Packages (Top Level)";
                                      GrandCtn := GrandCtn + tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine1[i]."Packages (Lower Level)";
                                      IF BillOfLadingInfoLine.NEXT = 0 THEN
                                        i := Lines;
                                    END;

                                  IF CarrierInfoCNT >= Number THEN
                                    FOR i := 1 TO Lines DO BEGIN
                                      tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine[i].TRANSFERFIELDS(CarInfoBillOfLadingInfoLine);
                                      tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine[i]."Line No." := CarInfoBillOfLadingInfoLine."Line No." + 1;
                                      tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine[i].INSERT;
                                      IF tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine[i]."Hazardous Material" THEN
                                        HM[i] := 'X';
                                      GrandHandlingQty := GrandHandlingQty + tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine[i]."Packages (Top Level)";
                                      GrandPkgQty := GrandPkgQty + tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine[i]."Packages (Lower Level)";
                                      GrandWgtCarrier := GrandWgtCarrier + tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine[i].Weight;
                                      IF CarInfoBillOfLadingInfoLine.NEXT = 0 THEN
                                        i:= Lines;
                                    END;
                                END;
                                 }

    PROCEDURE IncludePhoneNo@2(VAR Address@1240030000 : ARRAY [8] OF Text[50];PhoneNo@1240030001 : Text[30]);
    VAR
      i@1240030002 : Integer;
    BEGIN
      FOR i := 1 TO 8 DO
        IF Address[i] = '' THEN BEGIN
          Address[i] := PhoneNo;
          i := 8;
        END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE ClearValues@1();
    BEGIN
      GrandWgt := 0;
      GrandPkg := 0;
      GrandHandlingQty := 0;
      GrandPkgQty := 0;
      GrandWgtCarrier := 0;
      GrandCtn := 0;
    END;

    PROCEDURE DeleteRecords@6();
    BEGIN
      FOR i := 1 TO 20 DO BEGIN
        CLEAR(tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine1[i]);
        tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine1[i].DELETEALL;
        CLEAR(tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine[i]);
        tmpBillOfLadingInfoLine[i].DELETEALL;
        CLEAR(HM[i]);
      END;

      COMMIT;
    END;

    PROCEDURE ReportLoop@3(VAR CustCnt@1240030000 : Integer;VAR CarrierCnt@1240030001 : Integer) : Integer;
    BEGIN
      IF CustCnt <> 0 THEN BEGIN
        CustCnt := CustCnt - 6;
        IF CustCnt <= 0 THEN
          CustCnt := 1
        ELSE
          CustCnt := ROUND(CustCnt / 15,1,'>') + 1;
      END;

      IF CarrierCnt <> 0 THEN BEGIN
        CarrierCnt := CarrierCnt - 6;
        IF CarrierCnt <= 0 THEN
          CarrierCnt := 1
        ELSE
          CarrierCnt := ROUND(CarrierCnt / 15,1,'>') + 1;
      END;

      IF CarrierCnt > CustCnt THEN
        EXIT(CarrierCnt)
      ELSE
        EXIT(CustCnt);
    END;

    BEGIN
    {
      2016-09-26 TPZ1693 TMEI
        Add shipping agent service to Bill of Lading report
    }
    END.

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function
